data.description: NEW PRICE!  Low Maintenance, stair free home in Woodland Estates. This one owner home features an open floor plan with good sized bedrooms, large closets, low threshold shower, water purification system and convenient stackable washer/dryer. You'll enjoy the country setting from the large breezy front porch.  Fruit trees shrubs and raised garden planters complete the back yard. There is an extra garage/room, mostly finished with it's own heat.  The garage door screen allows a nice view into the back yard. Seller used as a man cave and for big family gatherings & parties extending into the backyard. It could be whatever is needed, man cave, movie room, play area, bedroom.....easy to show, call today!!!
